  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nOn a node with no vc (a work around version with `is-ip@4.0.0` to avoid performance issue), this libp2p metrics function takes 17%\r\n<img width=\"1280\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-10-28 at 15 46 08\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/198545333-8cc49ee3-de09-4b48-a188-9260e982ba2e.png\">\r\n\r\n[1028_novc_work_around_is_ip.cpuprofile.zip](https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/files/9886783/1028_novc_work_around_is_ip.cpuprofile.zip)\r\n\r\nOn a lg1k, it takes more than 5% of cpu time\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1306\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-10-28 at 15 50 00\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/198546191-aefb9a18-4788-4174-8298-a0efe25d72c8.png\">\r\n\r\n[1025_lg1k_chacha20poly1305_no_mem_alloc.cpuprofile.zip](https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/files/9886810/1025_lg1k_chacha20poly1305_no_mem_alloc.cpuprofile.zip)\r\n\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nlibp2p-metrics should not affect lodestar's performance",
